(2, 'ANNOUNCEMENT: 29th Japan IT Spring Week 2020 Event IS TEMPORARILY SUSPENDED.', 'Hachinet is pleased to announce that the Prime Minister of Japan after considering the complicated situation of Coronavirus, together with the result of the negotiations with related parties, the organizer has the conclusion: Japan IT Spring Week 2020 event, expected to be held on April 8-10th, 2020, is officially suspended. ', NULL, 'announcement-29th-japan-it-spring-week-2020-event-is-temporarily-suspended', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', NULL, 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
