(42, 'The serious security vulnerability in phpMyAdmin can allow hackers to damage the database', 'The serious security vulnerability in phpMyAdmin - a MySQL database management application that can allow hackers to remotely perform malicious operations on the database, just by tricking administrators into clicking on a link.', NULL, 'the-serious-security-vulnerability-in-phpmyadmin-can-allow-hackers-to-damage-the-database', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Phpmyadmin, security vulnerability, database management application,Ashutosh Barot, CSRF vulnerability, MySQL, DROP', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
(43, 'What is Agile? What is Scrum? Some Agile project management tools you should know.', 'There are many standardized software development methods, and one of them is the Scrum model software development (What is Scrum?). This article will explain the most basic concepts as well as the core values of Agile so you can master it.', NULL, 'what-is-agile-what-is-scrum-some-agile-project-management-tools-you-should-know', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Agile Method, Scrum, 3 core values of Scrum, The benefits of Scrum, Scrum Team, Product Owner, Scrum Master, Sprint', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
(44, 'Solution for developing online conferencing Video / Audio call application', 'Before learning about technology, remember that you have ever used audio/video call tools such as Google Hangouts? Have you wondered how they make such a smooth video call website with so many people involved at the same time?', NULL, 'solution-for-developing-online-conferencing-video-audio-call-application', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Video / Audio call application, WebRTC, ICE, NAT, STUN, SDP, RTCDataChannel, WebRTC - P2P application, Mesh, MCU, SFU', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
(45, 'Outsourcing service - Human resources trend in 21st century.', 'Outsourcing service is instead of letting official staff finish task, we hire the external service. This service will assume a part function that the company want to decrease to invest in other strategies. ', NULL, 'outsourcing-service-human-resources-trend-in-21st-century', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', NULL, 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
(46, 'What is IT Outsourcing? And the advantages of IT Outsourcing service', 'Over recent years, IT Outsourcing service has become dramatically popular. However, individuals who are not experts in this industry, there is still a question of what IT Outsourcing is? So, What is IT Outsourcing? What are the highlights of these services? Let’s find out the detail of this service in the below article', NULL, 'what-is-it-outsourcing-and-the-advantages-of-it-outsourcing-service-2', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Vietnam Offshore Development, Vietnam outsourcing, Offshore development, Offshore development recommended', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
(47, 'OUTSTANDING BLOCKCHAIN APPLICATIONS IN REALITY', 'Blockchain technology was born and with its breakthrough influence has been creating a tsunami of technology covering all fields of industries from long-standing tradition to the latest technology applications. Here are the top outstanding blockchain applications that have been or are being implemented in countries around the world, which are expected to completely change the traditional way of present applications.', NULL, 'outstanding-blockchain-applications-in-reality', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', NULL, 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
(48, 'THE BEST AI TECHNOLOGY', 'AI marketing has been growing. Besides recently established companies in this aspect, technology giants like Apple, Google also witness a dramatic increase in AI research investment.', NULL, 'the-best-ai-technology', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'AI, artificial intelligence', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
(49, 'VIETNAM - THE PROMISED LAND OF OUTSOURCING SERVICE', 'Josh Lieberman isn’t surprised when Vietnam is considered to be an alternative replacement of China and India in outsourcing service, in light of increasing finances and employee turnover rate in those countries.', NULL, 'vietnam-the-promised-land-of-outsourcing-service', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Outsourcing, Services,  Information technology', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
(50, 'WHAT IS AI TECHNOLOGY? LEARN ABOUT AI TECHNOLOGY', 'In this article, let’s find out with Hachinet about what AI technology is, as well as its applications in our daily life.\r\nAI technology (stand for Artificial Intelligence) is a technology that simulates human thinking and learning processes for machines, especially computer systems. Those processes include learning (gathering information and rules for using information), reasoning (applying rules to nearly conclude or confirm), and self-correction. Special AI applications include expert systems, speech recognition, and computer vision (facial recognition, objects, or writing).', NULL, 'what-is-ai-technology-learn-about-ai-technology', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'AI, Technology, Deep Blue, IBM', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
(51, 'LEARN ABOUT MOBILE APP AND THE IMPORTANCE OF MOBILE APP', 'Mobile Apps are mobile applications that allow you to access the content you want on devices like mobile phones. Is used widely in marketing, what is the Mobile App term? And how many types of mobile apps? Let’s read with Hachinet to find out through the following content.', NULL, 'learn-about-mobile-app-and-the-importance-of-mobile-app', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Operating system, mobile app', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
(52, 'WHAT IS FRAMEWORK? LEARN ABOUT THE FRAMEWORK.', 'Frameworks are pre-written pieces of code, forming into a framework and packaged programming libraries. It provides the available features like models, API, and alternative elements to minimize the development of rich and dynamic web applications. The frameworks are like we have the frame of the house prefabricated with the basic foundation, you just need to build an interior as you like.', NULL, 'what-is-framework-learn-about-the-framework', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Web application, React-Native, mobile application, Android,', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
(53, 'WHAT IS A BACKEND DEVELOPER? HOW TO BECOME A BACKEND DEVELOPER? PART2', 'In the previous article, we looked at back-end programming, back-end developer tasks, and the tools needed for back-end development together. In this Part 2, let\'s explore the database system and other backend information with Hachinet.', NULL, 'what-is-a-backend-developer-how-to-become-a-backend-developer-part2', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Front-end developer, back-end developer, HTML, CSS', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
(54, 'WHAT IS MVC? APPLICATION OF MVC MODEL IN PROGRAMMING', 'MVC model is one of the names that you can’t know when accessing web programming. If you haven’t understood about this programming pattern, this article of Hachinet is absolutely a knowledge manual that you need!', NULL, 'what-is-mvc-application-of-mvc-model-in-programming', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', NULL, 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0),
(55, 'HOW TO LEARN RASPBERRY PI?', 'Raspberry Pi is a Single Board Computer or is called by another familiar name mini Computer.\r\nThe combination of an operating system computer and extensive development of peripheral devices (sensors, control devices, function modules, etc.) is an advantage of the miniComputer board including Raspberry Pi, however, this also makes beginner confusion, not knowing where to start.', NULL, 'how-to-learn-raspberry-pi', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Raspberry Pi,  Single Board Computer,  minicomputer', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', '2023-02-17 01:10:54', 2, 0);
