(57, 'WHY SHOULD WE USE AGULAR?', 'If you used to build several web apps, you must have heard about Angular, a Frameworks JavaScript that helps us to build full-featured web apps from the client-side. Angular initially was established by Google in 2010 with AngularJS version, then has had quite a foothold for a long time, Angular version 2 released in 2016 brought a remarkable transformation, a powerful tool for web app development on both Mobile and Desktop platforms. Currently, we have had an Angular 6.', NULL, 'why-should-we-use-agular', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Agular, framework, JavaScript, HTML, HTTP, Router, MVVM, models', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-03-03 03:32:55', 2, 25),
(58, 'RASPBERRY PI: DIRECT TWO-WAY COMMUNICATION BETWEEN PC AND RASPBERRY PI', 'Through this article, you will learn about several protocols and software that support file exchange between PC and Raspberry Pi.', NULL, 'raspberry-pi-direct-two-way-communication-between-pc-and-raspberry-pi', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Raspberry Pi,  SPC,  FileZilla Client, WinSCP, PC', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-03-03 03:48:56', 2, 13),
(59, 'Hachinet Vinh: 2 excellent female staff members obtained certificates', 'Hachinet congratulates 2 testers Nguyen Thị Ngoc and Nguyen Doan Minh Thao for successfully completing the Tester course at TesterproVN and bringing benefits to the company when deciding to join the course.', NULL, 'hachinet-vinh-2-excellent-female-staff-members-obtained-certificates', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'testers, congratulation, Hachinet Vinh', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-03-02 00:45:53', 2, 2),
(60, 'THE AI TECHNOLOGIES TO LOOK FORWARD TO IN 2020', 'AI is progressing rapidly in 2019. AI has been transformed in many industries, from hardware to software, from entertainment to games at lightning speed. And AI will shape the world and the future of technology, with the participation of visionary investors and entrepreneurs.', NULL, 'the-ai-technologies-to-look-forward-to-in-2020', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'AI, artificial intelligence, blockchain, digital, technology, 5G, 4G, machine learning,  computing, AR, VR, IoT', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-20 02:35:50', 2, 4),
(61, 'The Next Goal of Hachinet: Top 10 prestigious IT enterprises by 2021', 'Nominating top 10 IT enterprises in Vietnam will be the destination and future goals of Hachient Software\r\n\r\nFound in 2018, Hachinet has gradually affirmed its position with 3 offices in Vietnam and the US. Besides, with a growth rate of 150% annually, Hachinet is going to reach 150 employees by the end of 2020.', NULL, 'the-next-goal-of-hachinet-top-10-prestigious-it-enterprises-by-2021', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', NULL, 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(62, 'CLOUD COMPUTING - WHAT IS CLOUD COMPUTING? MODEL AND BENEFITS', 'You may have been exposed to cloud computing but you still do not fully understand Cloud computing - What is Cloud Computing? Cloud computing deployment models for individuals and businesses. So let\'s also learn about Cloud computing - Cloud computing in this article! ', NULL, 'cloud-computing-what-is-cloud-computing-model-and-benefits', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'computing cloud, hybrid cloud, public computing, private cloud, PaaS, IaaS, SaaS', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(63, 'WAVESHARE 4 INCH HDML LCD, 800X480, ISP GUIDE', 'Through this article, you will learn more about Waveshare 4 inch HDMI LCD, 800×480, IPS.', NULL, 'waveshare-4-inch-hdml-lcd-800x480-isp-guide', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Rasberry Pi, HDMI LCD, IPS, Rasbian, Offshore, Outsoure', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-19 21:05:42', 2, 1),
(64, 'WHAT IS THE IOT? IOT APPLICATION IN PRACTICE', 'This below article is everything that you need to know about the Internet of Things or shortened as “IoT”. The meaning of this term is about the extension of the Internet beyond the computer and mobile phone, connecting with everything, processes, and other environments.', NULL, 'what-is-the-iot-iot-application-in-practice', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'IoT, Internet, sensors, industry, data, RFID', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(65, 'WHAT IS COBOL? INFORMATION YOU NEED TO KNOW ABOUT COBOL PROGRAMMING.', 'To be more specific, Cobol is just simply a third-generation programming language and has the oldest use up to now. Cobol is a term derived from Common Business - Oriented Language was created by Grace Hopper one of the world’s first outstanding and talented women in programming.', NULL, 'what-is-cobol-information-you-need-to-know-about-cobol-programming', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Cobol, programming language, software, pros and cons', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(66, 'LEARN ANDROID PROGRAMMING: KOTLIN OR JAVA', 'Despite the undeniable renown of Java as a programming language, Android initially needed a modern language. Kotlin filled that gasp since it was announced as the official language for Android.', NULL, 'learn-android-programming-kotlin-or-java', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'kotlin, java, android, language, programming, pros and cons, APIs', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(67, 'WHAT IS A BACKEND DEVELOPER? HOW TO BECOME A BACKEND DEVELOPER?', 'There are three types of programmers in web development: back-end developers, front-end developers, and full-stack developers (which work on both front-end and back-end). If you\'re reading this article, you\'re probably interested in the backend of your website, what the backend is, what the backend developer is, and how to become a backend developer. You want to know.', NULL, 'what-is-a-backend-developer-how-to-become-a-backend-developer', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'API,PHP,Node.js,Javascript,Python,HTML,CSS', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(68, '5 REASONS THAT AUGMENTED REALITY IN EDUCATION IS CONQUERING THE WORLD', 'Augmented reality app education is one of the hot topics recently. New studies show that AR is increasingly relevant in education because it offers a variety of experiences and values for both students and teachers. Let’s find 5 reasons that augmented reality conquers our modern education system with Hachinet.', NULL, '5-reasons-that-augmented-reality-in-education-is-conquering-the-world', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'AR, Augmented reality, app, application, education', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(69, 'When do we need to outsourcing human force?', 'In order to devote all efforts to building and executing strategies, businesses need to optimize time and cash flow, requiring human resources to be streamlined to operate smoothly and efficiently, outsourcing is a solution.', NULL, 'when-do-we-need-to-outsourcing-human-force', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Vietnam Offshore Development, Vietnam outsourcing, Offshore development, Offshore development recommended, personnel solution', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(70, 'WHAT IS THE FRONT-END? WHAT SKILLS DO FRONT END PROGRAMMERS NEED?', 'You are interested in front-end web development, but don\'t know where to start and what skills do you need? Read Hachinet\'s articles below immediately to learn about the skills you need to become a lot-end developer.', NULL, 'what-is-the-front-end-what-skills-do-front-end-programmers-need', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'HTML, CSS, UI, UX designer, front-end developer, back-end developer', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(71, 'The best IDEs for PHP developer', 'When developing PHP, developers tend to choose notepad or notepad++ without knowing that there are a variety of useful IDEs which could help in managing project more effectively and quickly. Let’s find out these IDEs in the below article', NULL, 'the-best-ides-for-php-developer', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'PHP, programming language, back-end, IDE', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(72, 'What is outsourcing? Why do enterprises need outsourcing?', 'Currently, outsourcing is the format of choice for many companies to develop. For example, when choosing a counseling company, large and small businesses choose the Booking Agency as an effective solution. But do you understand the essence of outsourcing? Do you know what outsourcing is?', NULL, 'what-is-outsourcing-why-do-enterprises-need-outsourcing', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Booking Agency, Service Level Agreement – SLA, Outsourcing', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(73, 'WHAT IS A TESTER? WHAT IS TESTING?', 'In this article, Hachinet will introduce the definition of testing, who the tester is, and when to perform the testing process, and let\'s clarify two concepts \"Verification\" and \"Validation\" in testing.', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1. What is testing?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. Who is the tester? What is a tester?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3. When will the testing begin?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4. When will the testing end?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">5. Distinguish the Verification and Validation</span></p>', 'what-is-a-tester-what-is-testing', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'validation, verification, tester, testing, ANSI / IEEE 1059', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(74, 'WHAT IS THE EMBEDDED PROGRAMMING? WHY IS THE EMBEDDED PROGRAMMING INDUSTRY BEING FAVORED??', 'Embedded programming is a programming term for an autonomous system, it’s embedded into an environment or parent system. Those are systems that integrate both hardware and software. ', NULL, 'what-is-the-embedded-programming-why-is-the-embedded-programming-industry-being-favored', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'embedded, programming, RAM, ROM, MCU, EEPROM, FLASH, ADC, DAC, UART, I2C,PCs, PDA, Linus, Windows, software, hardware', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(75, 'Hachinet JSC particpated in VIM EXPO 2020', 'On December 9th, 𝐇𝐀𝐂𝐇𝐈𝐍𝐄𝐓 𝐉𝐒𝐂 anticipated in 𝐕𝐈𝐌 𝐄𝐗𝐏𝐎 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟎 at International Exhibition Center I.C.E Hanoi - Cultural Friendship Palace, 91 Tran Hung Dao Street, Tran Hung Dao Ward, Hoan Kiem District, Hanoi, Vietnam. 𝐕𝐈𝐌 𝐄𝐗𝐏𝐎 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟎 - the biggest trading event of Technological Support -  Manufacturing and Processing Industry in Hanoi in 2020.', NULL, 'hachinet-jsc-particpated-in-vim-expo-2020', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'event, outsourcing, 𝐕𝐈𝐌 𝐄𝐗𝐏𝐎 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟎', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
