(154, 'Building EC Apps with Django | Introducing Django (Part 1)', 'Python is known as a very popular programming language in the technology world. Born in the late 1980s, it is named after Monty Python, who is considered the father of the language. Web programming using Python quickly became popular. The tendency to learn Django – Web Framework, an application specialized in web design for the Python programming language, is becoming more and more common.', '<p><a href=\"#h_29073849311631867434914\">1. Overview&nbsp;</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_389623003111631867439193\">2. Project initialization</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_640056509201631867443433\">3. Connect to MySQL</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_988524547281631867447960\">4. Docker for the project</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_568823977351631867452689\">5. Static and media settings</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_709550026411631867460233\">6. Customize user models, categories, and product models</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_816886648461631867465041\">7. Cart design, CartItem model</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_129016461501631867470641\">8. Home, store, product_detail templates</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_546325954531631867476025\">9. Summary</a></p>', 'building-ec-apps-with-django-introducing-django-part-1', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
