(174, 'Advantages and difficulties of offshore development in Vietnam', 'When it comes to offshore development, many people generally think of the cost merit of being \"cheap.\" However, in recent years, that aspect has changed. There are various factors, for example, due to economic growth in Vietnam and fluctuations in the supply-demand balance for IT human resources globally, including Japan, the cost merit is relatively shrinking compared to before. Rather, in recent years, the expansion of IT-related markets and the lack of resources have led to increasing attention to resource benefits.', '<p><a href=\"#h_30214260521638160586084\">1. Introduction</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_494952237181638160591867\">2. Reasons why Vietnam is often selected as an offshore destination</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_427608162331638160597011\">2.1&nbsp;Vietnam is a pro-Japanese country</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_330447488471638160602507\">2.2 Cost</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_855975707601638160608731\">2.3 Abundant and excellent engineer resources</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_58190022721638160615219\">2.4 Easy to handle development under various conditions</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_862376192831638160621363\">3. Issues/problems of offshore development</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_106577905931638160627483\">3.1 Communication may be difficult</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_4462248941021638160634819\">3.2 Differences in perception are likely to occur due to differences in culture</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_5688227841101638160709170\">4. Measures to prevent offshore development from failing</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_730681781171638160716769\">4.1 Understanding the differences in communication culture</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_730681781171638160716769\">4.1 Start a test team offshore</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p