(175, 'Commonly used languages for Android software', 'There are different types of platforms with their own strengths and weaknesses, and languages that can be developed differently. A good understanding of the characteristics of the platform and development language is important for successful app development. Therefore, in this article, we will introduce their features, advantages, and disadvantages in an easy-to-understand manner so that even those who have no experience as an engineer or beginners can create Android software.', '<p><a href=\"#h_96355132211637134664367\">1. Java</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_178874040101637134671248\">2. Kotlin</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_159635293181637134676102\">3. C++</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_240495692251637134683518\">4. C#</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_840011175311637134688749\">5. Python</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_45425358361637134693669\">6. Corona&nbsp;Native</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_187814499401637134698806\">7. HTML, CSS, JavaScript</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_512418086431637134704357\">8. Conclusion</a></p>', 'commonly-used-languages-for-android-software', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Android Software, Languages', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(176, 'ASP Overview | ASP Roles and Functions in IT', 'ASP is an abbreviation for \"application service provider\". It is a mechanism that puts the program data for executing the software in the cloud on the Internet, accesses the program data through the Internet line, and makes the software available.', '<p><a href=\"#h_33024362611640589152941\">1. Basic knowledge of ASP</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_113372207131640589159305\">2. Main features of ASP</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_198170690241640589168609\">・ There is no need to prepare a management system</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_717484394341640589179408\">・ Cost reduction</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_854379227431640589187863\">・ Easy to use</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_229852767511640589195235\">・ Operation is possible if there is a network environment</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_374520391581640589204251\">3. Precautions to know before introducing ASP</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_291521193641640589211541\">・ Internet environment is essential</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_632548426731640589228538\">・ Confirmation of functions and standards</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_300320598801640589237193\">・ Security depends on the provider</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_261068020831640589249320\">4. Summary</a></p>', 'asp-overview-asp-roles-and-functions-in-it', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Advantages and Disadvantages, An Outsourcing Company, Tester, ASP', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
