(186, '.NET Outsourcing Development Service Overview', 'The framework provides a consistent environment for object-oriented programming that works in the same way. Whether the code is hosted and executed locally, hosted and executed remotely, or stored and executed locally on the network, it provides an environment for code execution that significantly eliminates software deployment and version conflicts.', '<p><a href=\"#h_12216056211629106786062\">1. The good features of the .NET framework</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_227724873181629106793331\">2. Overview of .NET 5</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_944141774431629106803757\">2.1. Why is .NET 5 chosen?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_983787287661629106811987\">2.2. Technologies Available in .NET 5</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_8375226051101629106823542\">2.3. Technology ported to .NET 5</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_998149581291629106834155\">2.4. Alternatives to currently popular technologies</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_6475224741381629106842435\">3. Hachinet Software\'s .NET development service</a></p>', 'net-outsourcing-development-service-overview', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', '.NET, .NET Framework, api, clr, Framework Class Library, install, essential, microsoft', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(187, 'Software technology and Software development process ｜HACHINET SOFTWARE', 'When we talk about computer programming, we talk about coding in programming languages like Java, C#, C++, Python, etc., but also the software development process.  Merely learning how to code in a programming language is not enough to be a skilled Software Developer. It would help if you comprehended how to design a program under the OOP, SOLID principles. Then you will not just be a coder who always only knows how to program but will become a developer with decent knowledge in many fields.', NULL, 'software-technology-and-software-development-process-hachinet-software', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'software, development, process, coder, programmer, developer, engineer, coding, testing, analysis, operation', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(188, 'Hachinet Software\'s strengths in smartphone app development', 'Smartphones have become indispensable for people. For example, many companies are encouraged to use their mobile phones in-house, unlike mobile phones were banned previously. Therefore, employees get the job done effectively.', '<p><a href=\"#h_57879581811629099714207\">1. Characteristics of Vietnamese human resources</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_68192410791629099720377\">2. Worries about using the service</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_453747056161629099728018\">3. Hachinet\'s strengths in smartphone app development</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_548710749221629099734578\">4. What does Hachinet Software have?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_533249784271629099742584\">5. What will you get?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_825127011311629099750318\">6. Hachinet Software development technology</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_483413492341629099757809\">7. Application developed by Hachinet Software</a></p>', 'hachinet-software-s-strengths-in-smartphone-app-development', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(189, 'Lab-type Development | Vietnam Offshore Development Hachinet Software', 'Lab-like development is the hiring of a team of technicians over a period of time to develop and operate a software project. During the contract period, all lab personnel will be managed and coordinated by you. The lab type is suitable for long-term projects and is suitable for projects that need to be changed frequently according to requirements, operational projects, and projects that require stable technicians to accumulate know-how about the project.', '<p><a href=\"#h_93663065911631863953547\">1. Problems in the process of system development</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_50220465381631863957873\">2. What is lab-type development?</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_40072765141631863963217\">3. Why the lab development is chosen?</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_841034707191631863968753\">4. Reasons to work with Hachinet</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_785884673231631863973849\">5. Example of lab-type development of Hachinet Software</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_917259164261631863978609\">6. Conclusion</a></p>', 'lab-type-development-vietnam-offshore-development-hachinet-software', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Lab Development, Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(190, 'What are RPA and the difference between RPA and AI?', 'Many people have asked about the difference between Robotic Process Automation (RPA) and Artificial Intelligence (AI). Some even assume that those are similar. To those who aren’t familiar with these terms, these words seem to be incomprehensible and perhaps ominous to pay the hefty price tag of buying unwanted software products. To help you comprehend, we have gathered all the highlight features to show the difference between RPA and AI.', NULL, 'what-are-rpa-and-the-difference-between-rpa-and-ai', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'rpa, ai, difference, bpm, algorithm, data, digitalization, robot, digital', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(191, 'What is a project management tool? Introducing the necessity and how to choose', 'In project management, monitoring and operations, there are various elements, knowledge and information that need to be processed and organized in order to complete the project as quickly and stably as possible.\r\nFurthermore, the project management tool is a tool for smoothly managing the progress of the project and completing the work in a planned manner.\r\nIt has a variety of functions, such as reducing the time and effort of managing multiple projects and instantly sharing information between members. This article gives a brief introduction to project management tool software to simplify management', '<p><a href=\"#h_780113875251660638424399\">1. What is a project management tool?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_962620621731660638429894\">2. Necessity of project management tools</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_803547031191660638442889\">3. Basic functions of project management tools</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_4004209291841660638448690\">3.1. Task management function</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_9419454722251660638454865\">3.2. Reporting function</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_9463529932641660638459360\">3.3. Schedule management function</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_2482658013011660638466082\">4. Advantages and disadvantages of using project management tools</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_8452836913361660638471835\">4.1. Advantages of using project management tools</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_977406813691660638479935\">4.2. Disadvantages of using project management tools</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_1062467384001660638492244\">5. How to choose the right project management tool</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_3364160404431660638501029\">5.1. Identify Problems Facing Project Management</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_9006951314961660638516816\">5.2. Find software based on your company\'s actual needs</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_7027904465331660638525272\">5.3. Select project management software based on the current budget</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_1878452965671660638531809\">5.4. Consideration</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_881727025981660638558085\">5.5. Filter Software and Test It Many Times Before Buying</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_8765700666621660638568175\">6. 5 Recommended Project Management Tools</a></p>', 'what-is-a-project-management-tool-introducing-the-necessity-and-how-to-choose', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Project Management Tools', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(192, 'What to look out for before hiring an ODC company and how to set up an ODC?', 'Hachinet has shown you the pros and cons and the ODC\'s brief introduction and the difference between outsourcing and offshore in the previous article. Today, Hachinet will show you what to look out for before hiring an ODC company and how to establish it.', '<p><a href=\"#h_19877010311624446560639\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1. Three things to note before hiring an ODC company</span></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_45842957371624446565021\">1.1. Quality and skills</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_693836686121624446569293\">1.2. Portfolio</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_387206558161624446574181\">1.3. Communication</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_385713292191624446589512\">2. Offshore Development Centre Setup: How to establish ODC</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_466412628211624446594332\">3. Conclusion</a></p>', 'what-to-look-out-for-before-hiring-an-odc-company-and-how-to-set-up-an-odc', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'odc, offshore development center, establishment, setup, notes,', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(193, 'Gluon Mobile: Another cross-platform mobile app development framework', 'Gluon may still be new to everyone, but if JavaFX is a good candidate to replace Java Swing in the future, JavaFX may probably be more familiar to programmers. In addition, it\'s a mechanism that makes it possible to develop apps for android and iOS with a single code using Java. JavaFX is Gluon.', '<p><a href=\"#h_26792060211639393725347\">1. What is Gluon?</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_10270600951639393730170\">2. Gluon Mobile</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_21233795211642414681893\">3. Learn Gluon</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_443914254101639393740626\">4. Conclusion</a></p>', 'gluon-mobile-another-cross-platform-mobile-app-development-framework', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Gluon Mobile', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(194, 'What is the difference between upstream and downstream processes in software development?', 'System development involves several steps, ranging from customer interviews to proper construction. The first half of the procedure is referred to as the \"upstream process,\" but if there are many flaws or misunderstandings in the upstream process, many problems will arise in the second half of the procedure, referred to as the \"downstream process.\" The importance of management and the upstream and downstream processes of system development are discussed in this article.', '<p><a href=\"#h_79072742961664181168278\">1. Upstream and downstream in the manufacturing process</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_91547676151664181173735\">2. Software dependencies upstream and downstream</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_371720630221664181178857\">3. Open source projects in the upstream and downstream</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_843452012271664181184867\">4. Micro (upstream and downstream) services</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_670863966301664181190340\">5. Conclusion</a></p>', 'what-is-the-difference-between-upstream-and-downstream-processes-in-software-development', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Upstream, Downstream, Software Development', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(195, '오프쇼어 개발 센터가 무엇인가｜What is the Offshore Development Center?　', '오프쇼어 소프트웨어 개발 추세가 계속 증가함에 따라 오프쇼어 개발 센터(ODC)에 대한 수요도 증가하고 있다.많은 IT 기업들에게 ODC는 더 이상 생소한 용어가 아니었고 비용 효율성과', '<p><a href=\"#h_94458963891663122791904\"> 　1. 오프쇼어 개발 센터 개념</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_582295962201663122802271\"> 　2. 오프쇼어와 아웃소싱 비교</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_801739144251663122808096\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">　3. ODC의 장점과 단점</span></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_959259523291663122813736\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">　4. ODC를 설정하는 방법</span></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'what-is-the-offshore-development-center', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet , 오프쇼어 개발, 베트남 개발, 시스템 개발, 오프쇼어, 아웃소, 앱 개발', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(196, 'How to Avoid 8 Common Website Optimization Mistakes', 'Do you own a business or website and want to know how to improve the speed and bounce rate of your site? When you examine your website analytics, do you notice any red flags? Do you notice that users leave your website because it takes too long to load? Is it operational, and are visitors spending more time on your website? All of these indicators suggest that website optimization is off track, which simply means that you must begin optimizing your website immediately.', '<p><a href=\"#h_410450410121663058635416\">1. The website is not optimized for mobile devices</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_861855616341663058648477\">2. Loading times are slow</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_603141241531663058655248\">3. Lack of new business website content</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_696270510701663058661523\">4. Navigation is perplexing</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"5\">5. Avoid SEO</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_64826060941663058684500\">6. Stuffing Keywords</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_5014253201081663058691081\">7. Your images should not be optimized</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_5716469281191663058699655\">8. Do not track website traffic</a></p>', 'how-to-avoid-8-common-website-optimization-mistakes', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Website Optimization Mistakes', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(197, '오프쇼어 개발 센터가 필요한 이유는 무엇인가? ODC의 장점과 단점에 대한 간략한 소개｜Why do you need an offshore development center?', 'ODC', '<p><a href=\"#h_54577793711662448057677\">⓵ 오프쇼어 개발 센터란 무엇인가?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_712720230201662448062861\">⓶ 아웃소싱과 오프쇼어의 차이점</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_530983585411662448068533\">⓷ ODC의 핵심 인력</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_700641054581662448074933\">⓸ ODC를 구축해야 하는 이유는 무엇인가?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_254271324831662448080445\">⓹ 보안 위험</a></p>', 'odc-why-do-you-need-an-offshore-development-center', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet , 오프쇼어 개발, 베트남 개발, 시스템 개발, 오프쇼어, 아웃소, 앱 개발', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(198, 'Software Engineering-SDLC V Model -【Hachinet】', 'The V-model is an SDLC model where processes\' execution happens sequentially in a V-shape. It is also known as the Verification and Validation model. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThe V-Model is an extension of the waterfall model and is based on the association of a testing phase for each corresponding development stage. This means that for every single step in the development cycle, there is a directly associated testing phase. This is a highly-disciplined model and the next phase starts only after the completion of the previous phase.', '<p><a href=\"#h_800006079121661764195734\">1. V model</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_729324121441661764212021\">1.1. Verification phase</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_264622932641661764217505\">1.2. Validation phase</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_940261508811661764225550\">1.3. Design phase</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_8648574861171661764242649\">1.4. Test phase</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_9159262891371661764288430\">1.5. Principles of the V model</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_7914963931731661764300207\">2. Key Characteristics of Effective Software Development</a></p>', 'software-engineering-sdlc-v-model-hachinet', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, SDLC V Model', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(199, 'ODC 회사를 고용하기 전에 무엇을 확인하고 ODC를 설정하는 방법은 무엇인가?', '오프쇼어 개발센터 \'ODC\'에 따르면 오프쇼어 회사의 특징은 높은 기술과 낮은 개발비용이다. 오프쇼어 개발센터의 경우 인도, 베트남 등의 엔지니어들을 활용하여 시스템을 개발하고 있다.', '<p><a href=\"#h_587954705451661156173043\">I. ODC 회사를 고용하기 전에 주의해야 할 세 가지 사항</a></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <a href=\"#h_125226570101661156041544\">1.1. 품질 및 기술</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <a href=\"#h_622796929181661156048488\">1.2. 포트폴리오</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <a href=\"#h_379801949251661156055408\">1.3. 의사소통</a></span></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_523019724311661156061648\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">II. 오프쇼어 개발센터 구축: ODC 구축 방법</span></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_22405484361661156072984\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">III. 결론</span></a></p>', 'odc-odc', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet , 오프쇼어 개발, 베트남 개발, 시스템 개발, 오프쇼어, 아웃소, 앱 개발', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
