(209, 'What is the role of on-site members? The advantages and disadvantages of onsite services!', 'Onsite support is to have members permanently stationed at customers in the USA. In addition to offshore development services that optimize time and cost, we can provide on-site services that meet the diverse needs of our customers by taking advantage of being residents.', '<p><a href=\"#h_30927921911652772405148\">1. Role of onsite members</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_93702315281652772409698\">2. On-site member structure</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_597979320141652772413762\">3. Effective delivery pattern of on-site members</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_322746169191652772418730\">4. Advantages and disadvantages of on-site development</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_669702362231652772423346\">5. Hachinet supports both offshore and onsite.</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_759707991261652772427842\">6. Summary</a></p>', 'what-is-the-role-of-on-site-members-the-advantages-and-disadvantages-of-onsite-services', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, The advantages And Disadvantages, Onsite Services', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(210, 'What is software architecture? Tools, patterns and design', 'Much of what you do daily, from using your cell phone to sending email, depends on your system\'s software architecture. We often take software architecture for granted, and many people don\'t even know what it is or how it can be used.', '<p><a href=\"#h_519001140101656399476556\">1. Definition of software architecture</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_112099950281656399483344\">2. Why is software architecture so important?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_158720102431656399489552\">3. Software architecture in software engineering</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_96546611581656399495062\">4. Software architecture design tool</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_750954575691656399500977\">5. Software architecture pattern</a></p>', 'what-is-software-architecture-tools-patterns-and-design', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Software Architecture', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(211, 'Why choose Vietnam to hire offshore developers?', 'There is a surge in the tendency of IT companies around the world to hire offshore developers, which results in cost savings and productivity gains. Compared to Eastern Europe and East Asian countries, Vietnam has emerged as a relatively new market with affordable costs, well-trained IT workers, and more supportive policies. ', '<p><a href=\"#h_797657919711656575403425\">1. What is an offshore development center?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_9114843641021656575410022\">2. Why hire an offshore developer in Vietnam?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_9696323541311656575420298\">2.1. Advanced expertise of Vietnamese developers</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_7607320711561656575431227\">2.2. Government support policy</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_2145110381851656575437698\">2.3. Affordable</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_9961374982101656575444645\">2.4. High-end services and products</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_7948706722311656575451195\">2.5. Sharing responsibility</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_4187302282481656575459266\">2.6. Young and enthusiastic offshore development team</a></p>', 'why-choose-vietnam-to-hire-offshore-developers', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Offshore Developers', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(212, 'System design for millions of users (Part 2)', 'Designing a system that supports millions of users isn\'t a small challenge, it requires continuous improvement. Following system design for millions of users (Part 1), we will continue to explore ways to build systems that scale to millions of users.', '<p><a href=\"#h_186729372121650352390771\">1. CDN</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_484679220311650352398434\">2. Stateless web tier</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_867234443481650352404346\">3. Stateful architecture</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_684182711631650352410605\">4. Stateless architecture</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_429208466771650352415016\">5.&nbsp;Datacenter</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_125723230881650352420582\">6. Message Queue</a></p>', 'system-design-for-millions-of-users-part-2', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Authentication / Authorization Method, System Design', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(213, 'Authentication / Authorization Method | Hachinet Software', 'One of the most important issues in building a web application is how to verify a user\'s ID. Then, you need to understand two concepts: user authentication and user authorization. Let Hachinet show you how to create trusted digital transactions by implementing proper user identification and authentication methods.', '<p><a href=\"#h_83865043321649747194421\">1. HTTP / HTTPS</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_473511991281649747219680\">2. Session-Cookies</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_53905845531649747226814\">3. Token</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_806888622951649747585450\">4. OAuth</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_7786023941361649747591958\">5. Conclusion</a></p>', 'authentication-authorization-method-hachinet-software', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Authentication / Authorization Method', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(214, 'System design for millions of users (Part 1)', 'Designing a system that supports millions of users is not a small challenge, it requires continuous and continuous improvement. In this article, we will build a system that supports one user and gradually expands to millions of users.', '<p><a href=\"#h_46086110411648797968751\">1. Single system configuration</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_702319566201648797975870\">2. Database</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_609796529391648797982584\">3. Scale-up and scale-out</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_957160782541648797990385\">4. Load balancer</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_945737594851648798162117\">5. Database replication</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_269951050911648798168255\">6. Cache</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_593947551001648798175474\">7. Cache layer</a></p>', 'system-design-for-millions-of-users-part-1', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, System Design', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(215, 'Hachinet Software Company\'s Special Services', 'The engineers are made up of people from top technical universities representing Vietnam and people with practical experience in major companies who are proficient in the field and always realize high reliability and high quality. We provide high-quality services to meet the needs of our customers. Through the above, Hachinet believes that we can provide the best software service.', '<p><a href=\"#h_749868380111648707115864\">1. General</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_329833179231648707122169\">2. Features and appeal points of Hachinet</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_945584990421648707130614\">3. Hachinet is an offshore development company with a recruitment site in Vietnam - Devwork.vn</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_579191774521648707142887\">4. Provided services</a></p>', 'hachinet-software-company-s-special-services', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Offshore development, Special Services', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(216, 'Benefits of offshore outsourcing', 'In recent years, many Asian countries have become destinations for offshore IT outsourcing services. Simply put, it\'s much more affordable to pay employees in Asian countries than to pay employees in Europe or the United States. Offshore IT outsourcing allows businesses to operate fully at lower labor costs. This is especially important for labor-intensive businesses such as manufacturing and services where reducing labor costs helps reduce operating costs, increase revenue, and maximize revenue.', '<p><a href=\"#h_45309329211648629800388\">1. Cost reduction</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_35073764241648629807742\">2. Access to the world\'s most talented people</a></p>', 'benefits-of-offshore-outsourcing', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Advantages and Disadvantages, Benefits of offshore outsourcing', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(217, '[Outsourcing contract form] Everything you need to know', 'When outsourcing IT outsourcing, many people may have the following problems.\r\n\r\n\"I don\'t know how to conclude a business consignment contract because I have no experience of business consignment.\"\r\n\r\n\"What types of outsourcing contracts are there?\"\r\n\r\n\"I don\'t know how to proceed with the outsourcing contract.\"', '<p><a href=\"#h_139559089101658832724629\">1. What is the outsourcing contract form?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_338764496631658832755249\">2. Three main types of outsourcing contracts</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_301916865541658832749430\">3. Why are outsourcing contracts attracting attention?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_480071247341658832743647\">4. Summary</a></p>', 'outsourcing-contract-form-everything-you-need-to-know', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Outsourcing Contract', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(218, 'Benefits of DevOps for Enterprises | Hachinet Software', 'DevOps is a set of practices that combine agile software development techniques with rapid IT delivery to automate the process between the two and shorten the system development life cycle. DevOps works on the following principles:', '<p><a href=\"#h_82525287211655192064921\">1. What is DevOps?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_526132279241655192083700\">2. Key benefits of DevOps for enterprises</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_223448762361655192096245\">・ Better collaboration</a><br /><a href=\"im\">・ Improved speed and frequency of deployment</a><br /><a href=\"#h_137359370741655192117662\">・ Further innovation</a><br /><a href=\"#h_765333989831655192198699\">・ Defect detection at the initial stage</a><br /><a href=\"#h_7698983951051655192206887\">・ Improvement of customer satisfaction</a><br /><a href=\"#h_4866269741181655192415602\">・ Scalability</a><br /><a href=\"#h_4188145411291655192429501\">・ Service reliability</a><br /><a href=\"#h_9677844751381655192444327\">・ Stable</a></p>', 'benefits-of-devops-for-enterprises-hachinet-software', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, DevOps', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(219, 'Software development bugs: how to identify and prevent them', 'Powerful agile practices such as single tests, code reviews, and appropriate precautions for requirements can prevent or find bugs early on in the application life cycle.\r\nNo matter how talented the development team is, bugs are inevitable with all software coding work.', '<p><a href=\"#h_51715400511655278975049\">1. What are the types of bugs that usually occur in each step of the application life cycle?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_302309529121655278982961\">2. The reason why a simple project is too complicated to manage</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_659543331171655278988763\">3. What can you do to prevent this?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_559318870211655278995928\">4. What can be used to prevent the most common bugs?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_470180468261655279003979\">5. How do you prevent the occurrence of bugs in the first place?</a></p>', 'software-development-bugs-how-to-identify-and-prevent-them', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Bugs, Software Development Bugs', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(220, 'AI Trends and Latest Technologies in 2022-What do you expect from AI?', 'AI is already embedded in almost every aspect of everyday life. For example, Gmail\'s smart replies, Alexa in the kitchen, facial recognition on your smartphone, Netflix\'s favorite movies and Spotify music, and even self-driving cars.', '<p><a href=\"#h_99359336511650441662553\">1. Introduction</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_234082117211650441668846\">2. AI trends in 2022</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_3341083451650441675661\">3. How does AI solve the problem?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_249033182631650441683698\">4. AI utilization example</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_678689645891650441690686\">5. Conclusion</a></p>', 'ai-trends-and-latest-technologies-in-2022-what-do-you-expect-from-ai', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, AI', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(221, 'Vietnam IT Outsourcing Market | Growth and Movement 2022-2025.', 'Vietnam\'s IT outsourcing witnessed a sharp increase in market capitalization and growth last year (2021). This potential development may continue into 2022, creating many new trends in the industry. Let\'s take a look at how the IT outsourcing market will evolve in the next three years.', '<p><a href=\"#h_35464466611651648631525\">1. Vietnam\'s IT outsourcing market will grow and trend from 2022 to 2025.</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_281292336131651648636515\">1.1 Growth of his IT outsourcing market in Vietnam</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_344128827241651648641236\">1.2 Asia with the most outsourcing</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_664403851341651648646644\">1.3 Frequently outsourced features</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_824239502431651648662411\">1.4 Market with the most outsourcing</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_231209043511651648670227\">2. Future trends in Vietnam\'s IT outsourcing market</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_453790597581651648675068\">2.1 Remote work continues</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_990083034641651648680571\">2.2 Vietnam\'s IT outsourcing market</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_267994657691651648685835\">2.3 Asia as a Top IT Outsourcing Destination</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_349940476741651648691747\">3. Summary</a></p>', 'vietnam-it-outsourcing-market-growth-and-movement-2022-2025', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Vietnam IT Outsourcing Market, Growth and Movement', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(222, 'What is MVP Development? | Steps and Benefits Explained', 'The features and functionality of software products and mobile apps are fantastic. Traditional product development methods revolve around ideas, some of which are nonsense. There are numerous ideas that you would like to see implemented in your application, and it includes numerous features.', '<p><a href=\"#h_86940644101664784011849\">1. Low-risk and traditional MVPs</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_781038449271664784016424\">2. The MVP concept</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_660312986421664784022156\">3. The advantages of MVP development</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_924269983551664784027374\">4. MVP function prioritization procedure</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_978218889721664784044606\">4.1. It\'s required</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_760357599891664784049830\">4.2. It\'s ought to have</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_544542041961664784055638\">4.3. It\'s preferable to have</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_6198598951091664784067018\">5. Conclusion</a></p>', 'what-is-mvp-development-steps-and-benefits-explained', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, MPV', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0),
(223, 'Why You Need Single Sign-On (SSO): 6 Advantages', 'Customers want seamless access to various applications from anywhere, on any computer, as more organizations shift to the cloud. Similarly, most large organizations have hundreds of touchpoints with various labels, and attempting to manage them all can be overwhelming for IT staff.', '<p><a href=\"#h_848354064111662364400121\">1. What is Single Sign-On (SSO)?</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_896412429311662364405966\">2. Six Advantages of Single Sign-On (SSO)</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_235051399571662364826888\">2.1. Enhanced employee and IT productivity</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_285439357721662364832210\">2.2. Enhanced security features</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_482356599851662364838580\">2.3 When used in tandem with Risk-Based Authentication (RBA)</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_425947581011662364845531\">2.4. Eliminate password fatigue</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_1492235111101662364850553\">2.5. Simplified User Experience</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"#h_3582183601201662364855992\">2.6. Increased rate of software adoption</a></p>', 'why-you-need-single-sign-on-sso-6-advantages', 'imageblogs/PwgodMM8IS3BTjuL6UudAF0rBtaRgRuhFizqYAPj.jpg', 'Hachinet, Offshore Development, Vietnam Development, System Development, Offshore, Outsoure, App Development, Single Sign-On, SSO', 4, 'active', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', '2023-02-17 01:10:55', 2, 0);

