(7, 'IT recruitment platform HR Freelancer 23', 'Devworks is a cutting-edge platform designed to revolutionize the way recruiting companies and HR freelancer networks connect with the 4th industrial revolution in Vietnam. Developed by Hachinet Software, Devworks is the first-of-its-kind platform that is dedicated to optimizing costs while leveraging the expertise of HR freelancers across the country.\r\n\r\nWith a focus on providing HR freelancers with the necessary resources and opportunities to develop their skills, Devworks enables recruiting companies to source talent more efficiently, reducing recruitment costs and time. This platform allows HR freelancers to showcase their skills and experience to a broader range of companies, thereby increasing their chances of finding work and generating revenue.\r\n\r\nDevworks is designed to provide a seamless and intuitive user experience for both HR freelancers and recruiting companies. The platform is easy to navigate, and users can easily search for jobs, view project details, and communicate with each other in real-time. The platform is also equipped with a range of tools and resources, including analytics and data visualization, to help users make informed decisions and optimize their hiring processes.\r\n\r\nWhat sets Devworks apart from other platforms is its focus on optimizing costs without wasting human resources. The platform leverages the expertise of HR freelancers, allowing recruiting companies to save on recruitment costs while providing HR freelancers with the opportunity to generate income.\r\n\r\nIn summary, Devworks is a game-changing platform that connects recruiting companies and HR freelancer networks in Vietnam. With its user-friendly interface, comprehensive tools, and focus on optimizing costs, it is quickly becoming a go-to platform for both HR freelancers and recruiting companies. Developed by Hachinet Software, Devworks is a testament to the company\'s commitment to innovation and excellence in the HR industry.', 'it-recruitment-platform-hr-freelancer', 'Vietnam', '2023-03-01', 'vietnam', 'https://devwork.vn', 12, 'active', '2023-02-26 20:56:04', '2023-02-28 00:13:59', '200MM', 'Project labor', 'php,eee', 'Recruiter Registration\r\nSign up for Hr freelancer\r\nCandidate Registration\r\nApplication Management\r\nSchedule an application\r\nEmail & SMS Notification\r\nAPI Mobile Applications\r\nPublished Recruitment\r\nShow job vacancies\r\nBonus fee calculation\r\nCalculating salary for five candidates', 'Details Design,Coding,Testing,Deployment', '10', 'IT recruitment platform connects HR Freelancer.Devworks is a cutting-edge platform designed to revolutionize the way recruiting companies and HR freelancer networks connect with the 4th industrial revolution in Vietnam. Developed by Hachinet Software, Devworks is the first-of-its-kind platform that is dedicated to optimizing costs while leveraging the expertise of HR freelancers across the country.', 'er');

